compbench (2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Multi-architecture CI: build .deb packages for amd64, i386, arm64,
    armhf and armel using Docker + QEMU.
  * Update GitHub Actions to Node.js 24 (checkout@v6, upload-artifact@v5,
    setup-qemu-action@v4).

 -- Robin DUBREUIL <63008968+robindubreuil@users.noreply.github.com>  Fri, 17 Apr 2026 07:28:28 +0000

compbench (2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rewrite in C with direct kernel interface measurements.
  * Removed dependencies: python3, python3-psutil, pv, btrfs-compsize.
  * Compression ratio via statvfs, CPU via /proc/stat, disk I/O via sysfs.
  * Data copy via copy_file_range() syscall.
  * CLI redesigned: --zstd MIN-MAX range, --no-integrity-check, etc.

 -- Robin DUBREUIL <63008968+robindubreuil@users.noreply.github.com>  Thu, 16 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000

